{
  "texts": [
    "We now discuss how some of the antecedents of perceived usefulness and perceived ease of use in the TAM can explain our findings.",
    "In addition, we discuss the strategies educators perceived as ways to mitigate the perceived threats of AI adoption.",
    "In the technology acceptance model, computer self-efficacy captures the individuals' self-beliefs about technology and technology use (Venkatesh & Bala 2008).",
    "It is one of the antecedents of perceived ease of use.",
    "In the present study, it manifests in an individual's confidence or lack of confidence in using ADWTs efficiently and effectively to perform the tasks."
  ]
}